This is modified boot.scr from goldelico's download page. I have removed all
stuff and left just the graphics bootmenu so that it's always shown. You can
edit boot.scr.in and create boot.scr with this command:

mkimage -A arm -O linux -a 0 -e 0 -T script -C none -n "GTA04 Boot Script" -d 
boot.scr.in boot.scr